---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Automatizamos tu infraestructura en la nube"
  descripcion="Ingeniero DevOps con más de 4 años diseñando infraestructuras cloud escalables en AWS, Kubernetes y Terraform."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #EEF4FF 0%, #ffffff 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Columna izquierda -->
      <div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 border" style="color: #1E6FFF; background-color: #EEF4FF; border-color: #c3d9ff;">
          Automatiza · Escala · Optimiza
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-5">
          Infraestructura en la nube simple,<br />
          <span style="color: #1E6FFF;">segura y escalable</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
          LRA CloudOps te ayuda a diseñar, implementar y automatizar entornos cloud con las mejores prácticas de DevOps, IaC y SRE.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap mb-8">
          <a href="/servicios" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-opacity hover:opacity-90" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
            Explorar servicios
          </a>
          <a href="/blog" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
            Ver proyectos
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            Automatización
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            Seguridad
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            Alta Disponibilidad
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna derecha: logo en card -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-14 flex items-center justify-center" style="box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(30, 111, 255, 0.14);">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="LRA Cloud Operations" class="w-56 h-56 object-contain" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICIOS -->
  <section style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-3">¿Qué puedo hacer por tu infraestructura?</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-14 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #93b8ff;">
        Soluciones cloud de nivel enterprise adaptadas a las necesidades reales de tu negocio.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <!-- Cloud Architecture -->
        <div class="bg-white p-7" style="border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5" style="background-color: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h10a4 4 0 001-7.9A5 5 0 106 6.6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cloud Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Diseño e implementación de arquitecturas cloud escalables, resilientes y de alta disponibilidad.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">AWS</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Azure</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">GCP</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Kubernetes</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DevOps & IaC -->
        <div class="bg-white p-7" style="border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5" style="background-color: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">DevOps & IaC</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Infraestructura como código y pipelines CI/CD totalmente automatizados y reproducibles.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Terraform</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Ansible</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Docker</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">CI/CD</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Seguridad & SRE -->
        <div class="bg-white p-7" style="border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5" style="background-color: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Seguridad & SRE</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Hardening, políticas de acceso y prácticas SRE para máxima confiabilidad operacional.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Hardening</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Monitoreo</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Observabilidad</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Backups</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Monitoreo -->
        <div class="bg-white p-7" style="border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5" style="background-color: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Monitoreo</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Visibilidad total de la infraestructura con alertas proactivas y dashboards en tiempo real.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Prometheus</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Grafana</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Alertmanager</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Automatización -->
        <div class="bg-white p-7" style="border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-5" style="background-color: #EEF4FF;">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Automatización</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">Scripts, pipelines y workflows para eliminar tareas manuales y reducir errores humanos.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Scripts</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Pipelines</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Workflows</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TECNOLOGÍAS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-center text-gray-400 mb-12">Tecnologías</p>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-10 flex-wrap">

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/amazonaws.svg" alt="AWS" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">AWS</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/microsoftazure.svg" alt="Azure" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Azure</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/googlecloud.svg" alt="GCP" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">GCP</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/kubernetes.svg" alt="Kubernetes" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Kubernetes</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/docker.svg" alt="Docker" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Docker</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/terraform.svg" alt="Terraform" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Terraform</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/ansible.svg" alt="Ansible" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Ansible</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
          <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@latest/icons/githubactions.svg" alt="GitHub Actions" class="h-10 w-10" style="filter: brightness(0) opacity(0.55);" />
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400">GitHub Actions</span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
